{{term|term=[[Doppler effect]]|content='''[[Doppler effect]]'''}}{{defn|defn=The ''Doppler effect'' (or the ''Doppler shift'') is the change in [[frequency]] or [[wavelength]] of a [[wave]] in relation to an observer who is moving relative to the wave source.<ref name="Giordano">{{cite book
