{{term|term='''[[Regelation]]'''}}{{defn|defn=The phenomena of melting under pressure, then freezing when the pressure is reduced.}} 
{{term|term='''[[Relative density]]'''}}{{defn|defn=Relative density, or specific gravity,<ref name=specificgravity1>
{{cite book
